parameters: \N<Rozaro>Ah, how are you feeling? Is everything going well?

\N<Rozaro>Right, I've paid Yuia's preparation money to the person in
charge of the main unit today. This should ensure your
safety for a while.
\N<Rozaro>Mr. Rozaro? Don't make a mistake, it's 'Master'.

\N<Rozaro>Hmm... Speaking of which, today is the day Riia and the
others are coming. They should be arriving at the main gate
soon, aren't you going to greet them?
\N<Segi>With these clothes... I would stand out too much.

\N<Rozaro>I see, well, it's not Riia's first time here and he's with
the guard soldiers, so there's no need to worry.

\N<Segi>You don't need to be so formal, you know? This place is like
your home too.

\N<Segi>...I'm sorry for dressing like this. You probably don't want
to see your mom like this...

\N<Segi>But... it can't be helped. In this town, I have to live like
this...
\N<Segi>Did you make it here okay? Didn't get lost?
\N<Segi>I see... How about Rame-chan and the others?

\N<Riia>Rame-chan and Aunt Irime... they went straight to the usual
place as soon as they arrived here.

\N<Riia>Rame-chan and I... we promised to have a long talk after
everything is over.

\N<Riia>Your belly... it's getting bigger. Is it almost time for the
baby to be born? His baby.
\N<Segi>Is Lord Yuia... is dad doing well?

\N<Riia>I don't know. Rame-chan and Aunt Irime said they saw him
once inside the management office.

\N<Segi>Inside the management office...? I see... The two of them
were invited to Lyuda's banquet.

\N<Riia>More than dad, how about you, mom? Are you okay? Living here
with him.
\N<Segi>It's okay... I'm fine, mom can handle it no problem.
